{"id":13260,"date":"2022-03-17T14:26:00","date_gmt":"2022-03-17T07:26:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13260"},"modified":"2022-03-17T14:26:00","modified_gmt":"2022-03-17T07:26:00","slug":"hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/","title":{"rendered":"HYUNDAI CRETA 2022 CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C \u0110\u01af\u1ee2C RA M\u1eaeT T\u1ea0I VI\u1ec6T NAM"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Ng\u00e0y 15\/03\/2022,\u00a0\u00a0Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Creta th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n t\u1eeb 620 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m thu\u1ebf VAT).\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf tinh ch\u1ec9nh d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u00e0 Trung \u0110\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m, trang b\u1ecb k\u0129 thu\u1eadt ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u nguy\u00ean chi\u1ebfc t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Hyundai Indonesia v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u0103m 2023 sau khi nh\u00e0 m\u00e1y Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 2 (HTMV 2) ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Creta l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Hyundai t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Xe c\u1ee7a n\u0103m t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng xe c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a J.D Power. Creta lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 top nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu SUV b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 1 s\u1ed1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Nam M\u1ef9. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ra m\u1eaft th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi n\u00e0y, Hyundai Creta \u0111em t\u1edbi cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1 m\u1eabu xe \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh &amp; an to\u00e0n b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-11\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13266\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13266\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>1. Ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t<\/h3>\n<p>Hyundai Creta c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc D\u00e0i x R\u1ed9ng x Cao t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng 4.315 x 1.790 x 1.660 (mm) c\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m xe 200 (mm), chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u201cti\u1ec3u Tucson\u201d v\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t m\u00e0u \u0111en hay \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb LED d\u1ea1ng \u1ea9n. C\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ea5p, trong khi ph\u00eda sau v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111a gi\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-2\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13267\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13267\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1708\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-2-2048x1367.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Creta m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2 tone m\u00e0u c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u1ebb l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n. Hyundai Creta 2022 c\u00f2n trang b\u1ecb n\u1eafp capo m\u1edbi, b\u1ed9 m\u00e2m xe h\u1ee3p kim 5 ch\u1ea5u 17 inch hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u th\u1ec3 thao, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u00f2m b\u00e1nh xe c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, c\u00e1nh gi\u00f3 g\u1eafn tr\u00ean n\u00f3c xe v\u00e0 \u0103ng-ten v\u00e2y c\u00e1 m\u1eadp.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-16\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13265\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13265\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-16-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Creta n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u00e1c trang b\u1ecb: \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng full LED, \u0111\u00e8n phanh tr\u00ean cao d\u1ea1ng LED, tay n\u1eafm c\u1eeda m\u1ea1 Crom, g\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ebfu h\u1eadu t\u00edch h\u1ee3p xi-nhan \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 s\u1ea5y\u2026<\/p>\n<h3>2. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/h3>\n<p>Hyundai Creta s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n nghi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed c\u00e1c trang b\u1ecb ti\u1ec7n \u00edch m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch khoa h\u1ecdc, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-21\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13264\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13264\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1706\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-21-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i b\u1ecdc da, \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. C\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft da c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u nh\u1ef1a cao c\u1ea5p trong cabin xe gi\u00fap t\u0103ng th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n l\u1ecbch l\u00e3m. B\u1ea3ng taplo xe n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111a th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng 10.25 inch \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n \u0111a ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p camera l\u00f9i. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a xe h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 Mp3\/USB\/Aux\/Bluetooth, Android Auto, Apple Carplay v\u1edbi 8 loa Bose c\u00f9ng amply r\u1eddi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-28\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13263\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13263\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-28-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u01a1c trang b\u1ecb n\u00fat b\u1ea5m kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng Start\/Stop Engine c\u00f9ng ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh. Gh\u1ebf l\u00e1i xe \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n 8 h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 l\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh g\u00f3c cao, th\u1ea5p 4 h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 th\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i th\u1ecfa m\u00e1i nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m m\u00e1t nhanh v\u00e0 s\u00e2u t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u1ecdc kh\u1eed Ion, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng c\u1eeda gi\u00f3 cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch. V\u00f4 l\u0103ng xe t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c n\u00fat \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u1ea1c, nh\u1eadn cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n<p>Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb s\u01b0\u1edfi v\u00e0 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng minh, gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 MSLA, phanh tay \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed EPB v\u00e0 Autohold, c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u00e1p su\u1ea5t l\u1ed1p TPMS\u2026 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian ti\u1ec7n nghi b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac<\/p>\n<h3>3. \u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Hyundai Creta<\/h3>\n<p>Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng h\u00fat kh\u00ed t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y Smartstream 1.5L m\u1edbi, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 115 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 6.300 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat, m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 144 Nm t\u1ea1i 4.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat. Xe d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng qua h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 iVT (h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u1ea5p bi\u1ebfn thi\u00ean th\u00f4ng minh) do Hyundai ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-24\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13262\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13262\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-24-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u1ea5p IVT \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn t\u1eeb h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u1ea5p CVT th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a CVT (Ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i ch\u1eadm, ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, tr\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a \u0111ai s\u1eaft) v\u00e0 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a CVT (\u0111\u1ed9 m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, lanh l\u1eb9 trong ph\u1ed1).<\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 an to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u: ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3 c\u1ee9ng phanh ABS, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 phanh kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p BA, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i l\u1ef1c phanh \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed EBD, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ESC, kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c HAC. Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb 6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed an to\u00e0n, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi th\u00e2n xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1o b\u1eb1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 luy\u1ec7n th\u00e9p c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c AHSS \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n, gi\u00fap gia \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p x\u1ea3y ra va ch\u1ea1m.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/hyundai-creta-3\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13261\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13261\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1359\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3-300x199.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3-768x510.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Hyundai-Creta-3-1536x1019.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac g\u00f3i an to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu xe B-SUV, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng SmartSense tr\u00ean Creta. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh giao th\u00f4ng, \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n. G\u00f3i an to\u00e0n SmartSense tr\u00ean Creta bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m tr\u01b0\u1edbc FCA<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9 BCA<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1eef l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng LFA<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng tr\u00e1nh va ch\u1ea1m ph\u00eda sau RCCA<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n (Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 Cao c\u1ea5p) c\u00f9ng 6 m\u00e0u t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn: Tr\u1eafng &#8211; \u0110\u1ecf &#8211; \u0110en &#8211; B\u1ea1c &#8211; X\u00e1m Kim lo\u1ea1i &#8211; Xanh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Cao c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u00eam l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 2 m\u00e0u ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t (2 tone) m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng. Xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh 5 n\u0103m ho\u1eb7c 100.000 km tu\u1ef3 theo \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Hyundai Creta s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd Hyundai to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25\/3.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-creta-2022-chinh-thuc-duoc-ra-mat-tai-viet-nam\/all-new-creta-11\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13266\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13266\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/All-New-Creta-11-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h3>4. Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n<\/h3>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n l\u1ebb khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT):<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Hyundai Creta 1.5L Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n: 620 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Hyundai Creta 1.5L \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t: 670 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Hyundai Creta 1.5L Cao c\u1ea5p: 730 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y 15\/03\/2022,\u00a0\u00a0Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u m\u1eabu xe Hyundai Creta th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n t\u1eeb 620 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m thu\u1ebf VAT).\u00a0 Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u l\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13267,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[57,52],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13260"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13260"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13260\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13269,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13260\/revisions\/13269"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13267"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13260"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13260"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13260"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13260"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}